    "Researchers should focus on creating frameworks that help developers adhere to these policies while also fostering innovation.",
    "Although TrustAgent [63] delves into the complex connections between safety and helpfulness, as well as the relationship between a model's reasoning capabilities and its effectiveness as a safe agent, it did not markedly improve the development and deployment policies for agents.",
